/* Change the highlight color on scribd.com */

.highlight.highlight_highlight.selected{
    background-color: #ff0;
}
.highlight.highlight_highlight{
    background-color: #ffeb3b;
}

/* Adds highlight classes that I then can use around the web */

.highlight-sam-yellow{
	background-color: yellow !important;
}

}
